    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Vroom Vroom! Create the ultimate toy car race with the KidPlay 50 Piece Die Cast Vehicle Play Set! This set comes with 50 toy diecast race cars for boys in assorted colors, all of which are decorated like real race cars. In the set we&#039;ve included white, blue, green, yellow, orange, red and black toy cars in different shades and styles. Each car is painted in a cool race car style, and all are of a die cast construction. These cars are durable so they are ideal for indoor or outdoor play. Young kids will love zooming around and racing each other with this huge set of cars. This is a great gift idea for young kids and die cast race car collectors alike!</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">KidPlay Deluxe Die Cast Car City Set Racing Airport Military Fire Construction</h2>\n  <p>Vroom Vroom! Create the ultimate toy car race with the KidPlay 50 Piece Die Cast Vehicle Play Set!</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>Material:</strong> Die Cast</li>\n    <li><strong>Pieces:</strong> 50</li>\n    <li><strong>Colors:</strong> White, Blue, Green, Yellow, Orange, Red &amp; Black</li>\n    <li>Durable Construction for Indoor &amp; Outdoor Play</li>\n    <li>Painted Just Like Real Race Cars</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1000x1000/toys/509927_50pc_car_set_detail_01-v2.jpg\" alt=\"Vroom Vroom\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> KPDCCS</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 060886098317</li>\n    <li><strong>Color:</strong> Multi-Color</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>This set comes with 50 toy diecast race cars for boys in assorted colors, all of which are decorated like real race cars. In the set we&#039;ve included white, blue, green, yellow, orange, red and black toy cars in different shades and styles. Each car is painted in a cool race car style, and all are of a die cast construction.</p>\n  <p>These cars are durable so they are ideal for indoor or outdoor play. Young kids will love zooming around and racing each other with this huge set of cars. This is a great gift idea for young kids and die cast race car collectors alike!</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
    "short_description": "Vroom Vroom! Create the ultimate toy car race with the KidPlay 50 Piece Die Cast Vehicle Play Set! This set comes with 50 toy diecast race cars for boys in assorted colors, all of which are decorated like real race cars. In the set we've included white, blue, green, yellow, orange, red and black toy cars in different shades and styles. Each car is painted in a cool race car style, and all are of a die cast construction. These cars are durable so they are ideal for indoor or outdoor play. Young kids will love zooming around and racing each other with this huge set of cars. This is a great gift idea for young kids and die cast race car collectors alike!.",
